# Never commit a user's generated workspace or any real data.
# The plugin ships the engine (commands/skills/templates); the workspace is
# generated locally by /setup on the user's machine and stays private.
**/context/
**/accounts/
**/trackers/
**/drafts/
**/reports/
**/briefings/
**/calendar/
**/to-file/
*-Assistant/
workspace/

# Secrets / credentials — must never be in the repo
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
secrets*.json
credentials*.json

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
